<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RentEase | Terms & Conditions</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            background: #f4f6f8;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .intro {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .card {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .card h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .card ul {
            margin: 10px 0 0 20px;
        }

        .closing {
            margin-top: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .grid {
                display: grid;
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
                gap: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
    <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>
    <p>RentEase Platform Policies</p>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <p class="intro">
        These terms are designed to ensure safety, transparency, and a smooth rental experience for all users.
    </p>

    <div class="grid">

        <div class="card">
            <h2>1. Self-Drive Only</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>No driver provided</li>
                <li>Ensures privacy and comfort</li>
                <li>Full control of journey</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>2. Fixed Daily Pricing</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Charges per day</li>
                <li>No hidden costs</li>
                <li>Simple pricing model</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>3. GPS Tracking</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>All vehicles tracked</li>
                <li>Improves safety</li>
                <li>Helps in emergencies</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>4. Payment on Delivery</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Immediate payment required</li>
                <li>Prevents misuse</li>
                <li>Ensures commitment</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>5. Fuel Policy</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Return with same fuel level</li>
                <li>Fair usage policy</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>6. Availability Lock</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Instant booking lock</li>
                <li>No double booking</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>7. Digital Agreement</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>No paperwork</li>
                <li>Online acceptance</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>8. Late Return Penalty</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Automatic charges</li>
                <li>Ensures fairness</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>9. Rating System</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>User & car ratings</li>
                <li>Builds trust</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>10. Emergency Support</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Quick assistance</li>
                <li>Added safety layer</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>11. Damage Policy</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>User responsible for damage</li>
                <li>Charges based on assessment</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>12. Minimal Documentation</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Only essential documents</li>
                <li>Faster onboarding</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

    </div>

    <p class="closing">
        These policies make RentEase secure, transparent, and user-friendly compared to traditional rental systems.
    </p>
</div>

</body>
</html>